Repeat: P2, k2, sl 1 wyib, k2, p2
K2, p2, sl 1 wyif, p2, k2
p2, k2; drop slipped stitch to front of work, k2, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; p2
P2, k2, sl 1 wyib, k2, p2
K2, p2, sl 1 wyif, p2, k2
p2; sl 2 wyib, drop slipped stitch to front of work, slip the same 2 stitches back to the left-hand needle, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; k4, p2
